Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.64,0:00:21.40,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找尋著看不見的明天 著急地用手觸摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.60,0:00:25.91,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.06,0:00:38.50,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來是沒有出口的迷宮 就像需要解謎的拼圖一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.16,0:00:49.82,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有奇跡出現   夢想也將成為勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.01,0:00:54.94,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.09,0:00:57.86,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你的憧憬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.01,0:01:00.36,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  因為那份思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.47,0:01:03.65,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我了無形的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.89,0:01:09.73,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像稍微感受到了迷惘和煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.73,0:01:11.29,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論在什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.48,0:01:14.66,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.49,0:01:23.63,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  對你的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.62,0:01:28.59,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.92,0:22:24.19,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在心中綻放的玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.30,0:22:31.02,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗中燃盡  僅是一束火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.27,0:22:39.70,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在滿是隔閡的街上 如遊戲般的迷失自我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.81,0:22:43.95,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以小丑的心情躊躇著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.78,0:22:52.29,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要踐踏悲傷的殘片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.41,0:22:56.63,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人在未來中戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.21,0:23:04.77,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以解開今晚的謎底仍然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.05,0:23:09.23,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up！真面目  Hurry up！回到從前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.59,0:23:16.82,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is passion　兩個人的手中充滿的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.93,0:23:23.74,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入黑暗之中  想緊緊擁抱住陽光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.19,0:23:29.29,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在迷宮中相互Kiss
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.40,0:23:38.34,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁向樂園  僅差一道門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.50,0:00:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨著時代的演進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.90,0:00:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,困難的案件也與日俱增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.80,0:00:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然出現的是新一的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.10,0:00:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以柯南的樣子能夠應戰嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.30,0:00:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.90,0:00:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.00,0:00:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.40,0:00:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外交官殺人事件(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.20,0:01:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.40,0:01:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才打個電話過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.50,0:01:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還感冒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.40,0:01:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了新一 你給我快點回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.20,0:01:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.70,0:01:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫我身邊有一大堆難辦的案子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.30,0:01:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.90,0:01:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有客人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.50,0:01:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 下次再聊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.00,0:02:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要快點把感冒給治好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.30,0:02:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.20,0:02:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.50,0:02:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不打電話她會擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.60,0:02:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打了她居然掛我電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.20,0:02:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且淨發些牢騷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.30,0:02:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是搞不懂女人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.60,0:02:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你騙不了我的 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.30,0:02:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道那個傢伙就在這個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.80,0:02:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點把他叫出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.40,0:02:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.30,0:02:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.20,0:02:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點叫他出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.70,0:02:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.10,0:02:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南你怎麼也感冒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.40,0:02:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要亂動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.30,0:02:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南你跟新一兩個人怎麼搞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.20,0:02:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道現在流行感冒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.60,0:02:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤感冒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你既然不知道工藤在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會知道他感冒了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.00,0:02:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.50,0:02:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一剛才在電話裏鼻音聽起來很重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.10,0:03:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤打到這裏來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.50,0:03:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有的時候會打電話到這裏來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.90,0:03:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然你就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.80,0:03:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家所說的工藤的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.10,0:03:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.30,0:03:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情是誰說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.10,0:03:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的一個叫鈴木的朋友說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.10,0:03:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說工藤一直都沒有到學校去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.90,0:03:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是你把他藏起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.00,0:03:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,諸如此類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.60,0:03:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是那個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和工藤在電話裏說了些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.80,0:03:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跟我談起他最近看的一本有趣的推理小說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有就是J聯賽的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}J聯:日本最高級別的足球聯賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來就是問學校的同學最近怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.00,0:03:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 關於你的事情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.40,0:03:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.60,0:03:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你這麼一說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.40,0:03:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一好像每次都在說自己的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有問起我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.80,0:03:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.90,0:03:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.10,0:03:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.20,0:04:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他既然不時地會打電話過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.00,0:04:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少應該問一下對方的近況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.80,0:04:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得他是那種毫不關心你的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.30,0:04:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他沒有問起你的理由只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.80,0:04:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是工藤一定在某個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.30,0:04:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直注意著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.80,0:04:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想也許就在這附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.60,0:04:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.10,0:04:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在注意著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.30,0:04:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤他一定在哪個地方偷窺著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.00,0:04:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個小子還真是討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.90,0:04:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有自我介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.70,0:04:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫服部平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.00,0:04:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和工藤都是高中生偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.10,0:04:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高中生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.60,0:04:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 原來是個偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.40,0:04:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟 你感冒了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正好帶了一種好藥來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.70,0:04:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽你這麼一說我以前好像也聽說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.90,0:05:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關西有個非常有名的偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.10,0:05:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個被稱作關西的服部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.30,0:05:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一個則稱為關東的工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.00,0:05:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家常拿我們做比較
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.30,0:05:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.40,0:05:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是沒想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.20,0:05:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近都沒聽到工藤的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.10,0:05:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而報紙上也沒看到他露臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.60,0:05:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家還謠傳他已經失蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.60,0:05:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說現在關東就是我毛利小五郎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.50,0:05:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找新一有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.30,0:05:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼大不了的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想見見他而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.10,0:05:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關東現在就是我毛利…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.80,0:05:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要知道工藤新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.20,0:05:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是一個值得和我相提並論的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.30,0:05:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.60,0:05:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.40,0:05:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.10,0:05:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底給他喝了什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.10,0:05:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一種叫做"白乾兒"的中國酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.40,0:05:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在見到工藤之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.50,0:06:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都要在這裏打擾你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.00,0:06:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是見面禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.90,0:06:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請收下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有你這樣自做主張的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底要我在外面敲門敲多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們這家偵探社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.00,0:06:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真會接待客人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.70,0:06:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.90,0:06:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能請你們馬上聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.90,0:06:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您要調查您公子女友的品行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.20,0:06:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一份是她的照片和簡歷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.80,0:06:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桂木幸子小姐 今年24歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.50,0:06:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在三葉中學和三葉高中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.50,0:06:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都以第一名的優異成績順利畢業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.70,0:06:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前在東都醫學院念書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.20,0:06:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立志成為懸壺濟世的女醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.30,0:06:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對她有什麼不滿意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.30,0:06:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.30,0:06:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.70,0:06:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她太完美了所以看不順眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.50,0:06:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類本來就是一種多疑又善妒嫉的動物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到太完美的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.50,0:06:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會不自覺地想要找她的碴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.60,0:06:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說得沒錯吧 大嬸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.40,0:06:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.70,0:07:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我女兒的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.20,0:07:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詳情等你到了我家之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.60,0:07:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再跟我先生詳談就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.00,0:07:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.10,0:07:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就要過去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.90,0:07:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.80,0:07:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們夫妻一起來不就結了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才也跟你說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的先生可是個外交官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是被人知道他到這種地方來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.90,0:07:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會被媒體炒作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.00,0:07:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也跟你們一塊兒去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.60,0:07:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.90,0:07:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與其讓大叔一個人過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.20,0:07:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不如讓人家認為是我們父子去拜訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣比較不會受到懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.60,0:07:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.70,0:07:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.70,0:07:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你也一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.40,0:07:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幹嘛要去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.80,0:07:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多一個人去作伴不是更好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.70,0:07:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你去的話說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.10,0:07:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤到時候搞不好也會露臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.70,0:07:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們也一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你的感冒沒關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.80,0:08:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位哥哥給我的藥已經把我治好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.40,0:08:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.20,0:08:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.30,0:08:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反而更嚴重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.70,0:08:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不想去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.90,0:08:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果不管這個傢伙不知道他又會說出什麼話來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.40,0:08:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 您回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.70,0:08:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想老爺應該在書房裏面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.80,0:08:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這幾位客人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的一個老朋友毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.70,0:08:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來打擾您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.90,0:08:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是照片上的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會到這個地方來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.60,0:08:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我叫她來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.40,0:08:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是看老爸想要和幸子見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才硬逼著她來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.00,0:08:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子老爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.10,0:08:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才開始就一直沒離開書房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.40,0:08:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.40,0:08:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這幾位客人是母親大人您的朋友嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.40,0:08:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是都跟你沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.80,0:08:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.70,0:08:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為你還沒有資格對我稱呼母親大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.60,0:08:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請跟我來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.60,0:08:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個續弦有什麼了不起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.80,0:09:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 父親大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.70,0:09:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您有事情要跟我談嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.40,0:09:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.30,0:09:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是妳跟我說要聽我釣到那條大魚的故事嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.40,0:09:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 這條魚是不是很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.60,0:09:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確是蠻大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.40,0:09:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您先到和室那裏等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.70,0:09:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.50,0:09:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.70,0:09:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.10,0:09:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.10,0:09:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道不在裏面嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.90,0:09:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.70,0:09:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在書房嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.90,0:09:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 音響還開著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.00,0:09:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然就這樣睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.50,0:09:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是歌劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公 醒一醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.40,0:09:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點起來了 老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.40,0:09:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.70,0:10:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.40,0:10:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你醒醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.30,0:10:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.70,0:10:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大嬸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.80,0:10:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭 快去報警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.80,0:10:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.70,0:10:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死者身體還有餘溫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.10,0:10:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且他的嘴唇也正開始變成紫色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.50,0:10:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在他髮根的地方有一個小小的紅點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.00,0:10:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.90,0:10:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛 痛死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.20,0:10:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個小鬼怎麼會在這個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.10,0:10:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.50,0:10:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你沒有好好照顧他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.10,0:10:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以讓一個小孩子看屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.50,0:10:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這名死者叫做辻村勲 今年54歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.00,0:10:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個外交官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.50,0:10:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且在屍體被發現的現場正好就有一位偵探…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.70,0:10:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我毛利小五郎 目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.20,0:10:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.90,0:11:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這是一件謀殺案囉 名偵探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.50,0:11:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看他沒有明顯的外傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.30,0:11:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看仔細了 那具屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.60,0:11:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毒殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.50,0:11:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是 是毒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.80,0:11:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位大叔是被某人下了毒殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.70,0:11:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看除了在他的髮根邊緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.80,0:11:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留有一個紅色的小點以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.00,0:11:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屍體旁邊還掉落了一根疑似兇器的針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.50,0:11:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位大叔死的時候雖然手撐著臉頰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.40,0:11:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是依我看恐怕是被人用毒針刺死之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再故意擺出這個姿勢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.80,0:11:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這也可能是自殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.20,0:11:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到現在還不懂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.20,0:11:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看看這具屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.10,0:11:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死者的嘴唇和手指末端都已經變成紫色的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.80,0:11:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且眼結膜上還有溢血點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.60,0:11:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些也都是窒息死亡的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.60,0:11:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這裏根本找不出死者是被勒死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.20,0:11:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者是溺死而痛苦掙扎的跡象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.60,0:11:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此 最有可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是兇手用毒麻痹死者的神經後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.70,0:11:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令其窒息死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.51,0:12:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且用的是一種立刻致死的劇毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.60,0:12:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外 從死者身上還有餘溫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.30,0:12:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及完全看不出有死後僵硬以及屍斑的情況來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.00,0:12:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定是在我們進入書房前30分鐘之內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.10,0:12:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被某人給毒殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.90,0:12:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就被在這屋子附近的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.60,0:12:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某人給殺害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.60,0:12:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.60,0:12:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個少年到底是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.70,0:12:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫服部平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一個狂妄的少年偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.40,0:12:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服部平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.40,0:12:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.20,0:12:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是大阪府警本部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.30,0:12:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服部平藏的兒子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.40,0:12:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大阪府警本部長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.40,0:12:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個叫服部的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.20,0:12:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和新一好像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.70,0:12:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要緊吧 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.00,0:12:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.00,0:12:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的感冒越來越嚴重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.80,0:12:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,書房裏所有的窗戶都是從房間裏面反鎖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.70,0:12:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要從房間裏出去根本不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.10,0:13:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.00,0:13:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這扇門是唯一的出入口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們當中握有這個房間鑰匙的某人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.80,0:13:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是絕對脫不了關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.30,0:13:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.40,0:13:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個書房應該有好幾副鑰匙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.30,0:13:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.10,0:13:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有兩把鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.90,0:13:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一把就是我手上的這把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一把在我先生身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.20,0:13:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先生身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.80,0:13:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他平常都習慣把它放在褲袋裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.00,0:13:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我來確認一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.90,0:13:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的 褲袋裏鼓鼓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.80,0:13:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.40,0:13:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.70,0:13:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還不懂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.40,0:13:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們進來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.60,0:13:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這間書房的門明明是鎖上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.10,0:13:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.70,0:13:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手在犯案之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.50,0:13:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是把門鎖上之後才離開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.40,0:13:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這書房的其中一把鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.40,0:13:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在和我們一起進書房的夫人身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.80,0:14:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外一把則是在被害人褲子的雙層口袋裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.30,0:14:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就形成了完美的不可能犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.00,0:14:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是密室殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.50,0:14:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密室殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.40,0:14:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.20,0:14:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.50,0:14:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近刊登在報刊上的這個大叔的推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不是他的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.70,0:14:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是工藤新一的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.30,0:14:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的案件都是他解開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.70,0:14:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個昏庸的大叔偷偷和工藤聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋求他的協助而破案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.70,0:14:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一次估計也不例外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.90,0:14:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.90,0:14:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件密室殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底誰會先解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.80,0:14:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走著瞧吧 工藤新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.50,0:14:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.00,0:14:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在竟然開始耳鳴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子我最好早點把這個案子解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.40,0:14:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去睡個覺才是上策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.00,0:14:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.60,0:14:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,案發時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.60,0:14:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是在3點半到4點之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.10,0:14:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之現在應該儘快查出這段時間可能犯案的人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.30,0:14:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個才是最重要的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.10,0:14:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.90,0:14:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可別輸給他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.70,0:15:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你要讓這個外人兼毛頭小子搶先嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.20,0:15:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和平常一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都把希望寄託在你身上了 名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.20,0:15:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.90,0:15:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管家小池先生下午3點到4點之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.10,0:15:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在大門口和附近的鄰居聊天是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.80,0:15:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貴善先生和幸子小姐他們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.40,0:15:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是在辻村夫人回家之前不久才到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.80,0:15:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.60,0:15:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.80,0:15:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.40,0:15:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在小池先生到玄關迎接辻村夫人回家的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.50,0:15:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們到老爸的書房去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.00,0:15:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是書房的門鎖住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.50,0:15:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫他又沒有回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.60,0:15:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們很快就下樓來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.40,0:15:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下來之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.30,0:15:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就在玄關和母親大人見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.20,0:15:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 利光老先生到這裏來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.10,0:15:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是2點之後的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.00,0:15:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.30,0:15:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易到這兒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.90,0:15:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿勲卻關在書房裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.30,0:15:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公江她又出門去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.70,0:15:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.70,0:15:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就一直呆在書房隔壁的客廳裏看電視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.00,0:15:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼辻村夫人是什麼時候出去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是1個小時以前出去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.90,0:16:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.30,0:16:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在犯案時間內最接近被害人的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.80,0:16:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是除了小池先生和辻村夫人以外的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.40,0:16:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那三個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的CD數量還真不少啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.60,0:16:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們老爺向來很喜歡聽古典音樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.70,0:16:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古典音樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們剛才發現屍體的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.80,0:16:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,播放的明明是歌劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.30,0:16:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.00,0:16:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.70,0:16:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.90,0:16:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你問這個幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.20,0:16:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這張是20年前的照片了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.40,0:16:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛開始看不清了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.20,0:16:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.00,0:16:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桌子上的書該怎麼處理呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.40,0:16:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就放著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.70,0:16:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.80,0:16:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.90,0:16:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死者的面前的確是放著一整套的精裝書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.10,0:16:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是一大疊一起被從書架上挪下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.80,0:16:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被害人身上的這把鑰匙有點怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.20,0:16:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.50,0:16:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個鑰匙環打開以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.00,0:16:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裏面有膠帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙環正中間還有一條小小的空隙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.50,0:17:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓…讓我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.60,0:17:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.30,0:17:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一次換成胸口了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.50,0:17:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得快點把案子解決才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.50,0:17:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在應該有一點眉目了吧 名偵探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.80,0:17:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.10,0:17:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.00,0:17:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.40,0:17:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屍體前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.50,0:17:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擺得不自然的這些書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.30,0:17:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.20,0:17:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凶案現場播放的歌劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.80,0:17:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個黏在鑰匙環上的膠帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.30,0:17:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有正中間那個神秘的空隙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.80,0:17:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上這扇門下面的縫隙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.30,0:17:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.00,0:17:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.00,0:17:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.00,0:17:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這間密室的手法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.20,0:17:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.50,0:17:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.50,0:17:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.00,0:17:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.70,0:18:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點叫醫生來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.60,0:18:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒得好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.40,0:18:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部怎麼不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.20,0:18:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他剛才向我問了和室的位置後就出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.00,0:18:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.00,0:18:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.20,0:18:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我推理正確的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會在這房間的某處的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.60,0:18:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.60,0:18:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.40,0:18:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.60,0:18:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這場比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.10,0:18:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我贏定了 工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.90,0:18:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.10,0:18:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問這裏有沒有可以躺的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.50,0:18:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓他躺在我房間的床上好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.20,0:18:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的房間就在走廊盡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.40,0:18:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就打擾借用一下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.60,0:18:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.50,0:18:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.10,0:18:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密室的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.10,0:18:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及兇手是誰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.40,0:18:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.40,0:19:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已經解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.30,0:19:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這都要怪你太不中用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.90,0:19:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就讓你們來看看證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.60,0:19:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,釣魚線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.30,0:19:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.50,0:19:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.40,0:19:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能請你當一下死者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.40,0:19:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.50,0:19:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,案發當時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.20,0:19:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這書房裏的所有窗戶都是從裏面被鎖住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.90,0:19:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一可以出入的那扇門也用鑰匙給鎖住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.70,0:19:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來就形成了不可能出入的密室殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.70,0:19:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個看似安全密閉的房間裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.50,0:19:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還留有一條縫隙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.40,0:19:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,縫隙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.20,0:19:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.00,0:19:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那扇門下面的縫隙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.10,0:19:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會要說那個兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.40,0:19:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是通過這條縫隙把書房的鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丟進被害人的褲袋裏的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.20,0:19:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.50,0:20:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有膠帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.70,0:20:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我剛才找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.30,0:20:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這條用來綁鐵針的釣魚線就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.50,0:20:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,釣魚線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.40,0:20:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會有事的 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下下 醫生馬上就過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.80,0:20:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太沒面子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.70,0:20:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼重要的時候我竟然因為感冒而倒下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.90,0:20:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.40,0:20:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手就是這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.30,0:20:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先在被害人的脖子上刺進毒針將他殺害後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.90,0:20:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把被害人的鑰匙給拿走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.50,0:20:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.20,0:20:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他再把綁了毒針的釣魚線抽出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.40,0:20:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這根線綁住針的另一頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黏在膠帶上面加以固定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.60,0:20:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後將綁了針的一端塞進被害人的褲袋裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓釣魚線從中間通過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.70,0:20:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後讓被害人坐在椅子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.50,0:20:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓死者擺出被發現時手撐著臉頰的姿勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後只要握著釣魚線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.80,0:20:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從門口走出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.10,0:21:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以從門下的縫隙把釣魚線拉到門外把門關上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後用鑰匙把門鎖上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.60,0:21:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著把鑰匙放在地上再將釣魚線的另一頭拉過來就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.30,0:21:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.20,0:21:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙就會通過門下的縫隙爬上桌子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.30,0:21:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動地掉進被害人的褲袋裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.90,0:21:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進…進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.60,0:21:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後他只要再用力一拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.20,0:21:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能夠把釣魚線從膠帶裏抽出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.20,0:21:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後只要把線收好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.10,0:21:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣證據就消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.40,0:21:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此一個完全的密室就形成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.40,0:21:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確…確實如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.20,0:21:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要振作一點 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.80,0:21:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.20,0:21:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.70,0:21:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的心臟好像快要裂開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.40,0:21:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是醫生來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.80,0:21:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.70,0:21:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上去請他過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.80,0:21:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我會死掉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.90,0:21:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.90,0:21:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.20,0:22:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.50,0:22:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是對我的推理有意見的話就快點出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.70,0:22:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.80,0:22:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的謎團都要被我解開囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.20,0:23:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.20,0:23:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本不是這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.20,0:23:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他根本沒有殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.40,0:23:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.70,0:23:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.20,0:23:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說我的推理哪裏錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.40,0:24:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.30,0:24:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.00,0:24:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.00,0:24:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.50,0:24:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.20,0:24:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.60,0:24:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外交官殺人事件(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.40,0:24:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.40,0:24:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌劇的CD和書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.10,0:24:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.80,0:24:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.90,0:24:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是隔了14個月後回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.70,0:24:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我新一
